sequenceDiagram
    actor Applicant
    actor Caseworker
    participant Intake
    participant Workflow
    participant DataExchange as Data Exchange
    participant Scheduling
    participant DocMgmt as Document Management
    participant Eligibility

    Applicant->>Intake: POST /applications/{id}/submit
    Intake->>Intake: application: draft → submitted
    Intake-->>Workflow: intake.application.submitted
    Workflow->>Workflow: create intake_review task (SLA clock starts)
    Intake->>DataExchange: create service-call (subscription: intake.application.submitted)
    Note over DataExchange: Data exchange fans out per-member<br/>checks (FDSH, IEVS, SAVE, SSA)
    Intake->>Intake: create document checklist (subscription: intake.application.submitted)

    DataExchange-->>Intake: data-exchange.service-call.completed
    Intake->>Intake: write result to ApplicationMember.verifications
    opt serviceType=fdsh, result=inconclusive
        Intake->>Intake: create citizenship ApplicationDocument
    end

    Caseworker->>Workflow: POST /tasks/{id}/claim
    Workflow-->>Intake: workflow.task.claimed
    Intake->>Intake: application: submitted → under_review
    Intake->>Intake: create Interview record

    Caseworker->>Scheduling: schedule appointment (subjectType: interview)
    Scheduling-->>Intake: scheduling.appointment.scheduled
    Intake->>Intake: append appointmentId to Interview.appointments

    DocMgmt-->>Intake: document-management.document.verified
    Intake->>Intake: ApplicationDocument: requested → verified

    Eligibility-->>Intake: eligibility.determination.completed
    Intake->>Intake: write outcome to ApplicationMember.programDeterminations

    Caseworker->>Intake: POST /applications/{id}/complete-review
    Intake-->>Workflow: intake.application.review_completed

    Caseworker->>Intake: POST /applications/{id}/close
    Intake->>Intake: application: under_review → closed
